description:
Katsuragi Youko plays the part of Sister Rayer (Scarlett Church) in the "Cosprayers" show. She is quite the opposite of her rival Natsumi, for although she has confidence in her acting skills, she is unsure of her looks.
Her name is derived from Katsuragi Hikaru (桂木ひかる) of Choudenshi Bioman (超電子バイオマン) and Yagami Youko (八神洋子) of Gekisou Sentai Car Rangers (激走戦隊カーレンジャー)
name: Katsuragi Youko
